                <h2 style="color: rgb(32, 32, 32);">project RSF</h2>
                <p>This web application is rebuilt from a similar map like app I made in 2018, project RSF/RSA, both
                    this
                    and the previous one have same purpose, i.e. to identify life threatening locations and prevent
                    crime
                    from happening. Some inspiration was taken from <span>Plan International and Monash University's XYX
                        Lab's
                        work on Free To Be</span>. Although the main program from that project is no longer available,
                    some
                    portions of
                    the
                    research work is still intact, I was going to delete those last remaining files, but after observing
                    the
                    recent events that’s going on here, I have decided to publish a prototype for both users if it can
                    help
                    them to stay safe and for other developers if they can create something more useful for people.</p>

