                    created
                    a
                    very base model that focuses on eliminating the opportunity of perverts/people-with-malice coming in
                    contact with normal people…without this base even the predictive portions would be useless...
                </p>
                <p>In the previous project, I had tried using google trends to maximum capacity and the predictive model
                    was somewhat working, analysing past data along with news it gave some affirmative hits, like the
                    ones
